features: COMPATIBLE MODEL - The fire HD 10 case from is especially designed for Amazon Fire HD 10 Tablet, which is released in 2021 the 11th generation. Please be aware, this protective cover is only for 2021 Fire HD 10 Tablet, to make sure that you order the right protection cases for your tablet and save your efforts, please identify your tablet's model before purchasing.

THOUGHTFUL DESIGN - This fire HD 10 case is designed with magnetic closure, in order to provide your tablet a reliable protection for the screen of your fire HD 10 tablet as well as a 360° protection for your tablet. And also this tablet case can provide 3 ergonomic positions for a comfortable viewing or typing and it consists auto wake/sleep function, which will keep your tablet screen clean and easy for you to use. All you need to do is to enjoy the happy hour with your Fire HD tablet.

PERFECT CUTS - The great craftsmanship of our fire HD 10 cover is designed for Amazon Fire HD 10, the 11th generation released in 2021. With the precise cutouts, the protective cover provides a easy access to all the camera, buttons and interfaces of your fire HD 10 tablet. This fire HD 10 case will provide a full protection for every corner of your tablet and keep it from dust, scratches or other damage.

PREMIUM MATERIAL - The inner case of our amazon fire HD 10 case is made of firmly, durable PC material and the flip cover is made of high-quality microfiber material with canvas texture. The waterproof HD 10 cover weight only 10.2 oz, the lightweight and portable design makes it easier for you to carry your HD 10 tablet around, the whole protect case won't be a burden for your hands when you want to play your tablet for a long time.

MULTIPLE COLORS & GREAT GIFT - Amazon Fire HD 10 case for Fire HD 10 Tablet 11th Gen 2021 released is with multiple colors: charcoal black, sandstone white, twilight blue, plum, royal blue. You can choose it as a gift for yourself, friends or your family. Please check the package content upon receiving the product. If you have any question about the product, please don’t hesitate to turn to us, we are always ready to help you!
description: Amazon Fire HD 10 Case Compatible with Fire HD 10 Tablet 11th Generation 2021 Released. Protect your fire HD 10 tablet comprehensively and enjoy a comfortable touch everyday with protection case series. PLEASE NOTE: These cases are specially developed for amazon fire HD 10 tablet 11th generation, 2021 released, and they are not compatible with any other models of tablets. WHY CHOOSE FIRE HD 10 TABLET CASE TO PROTECT YOUR TABLET? High Quality Material The canvas textured flip cover is made of firm and durable microfiber and for ultimate holding comfort and moderate friction. Smart Fit With this cover your fire HD 10 is not only protected from two sides, but all corners and edges. The perfect cutouts allow for easy controls and access for all the camera, buttons and interfaces. Flip Cover Closure The magnetic closure of this tablet case allows the case to be securely closed to offer your tablet a comprehensive protection, won’t easily open itself when in handbags or backpacks. With Folding Stand The flip cover of tablet case can provide 3 positions for you to have a comfortable viewing or using experience. Lightweight & Compact Design Lightweight material and compact shape won't add too much burden for you to carry. Modern Style Elegant and modern, they are available in charcoal black, sandstone white, twilight blue, plum, royal blue, you can find you favorite color!
